(368, 1, '2013-07-02 10:53:36', '2013-07-02 10:53:36', '<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/sparkling-rose-eyes-romantic-curls_look_6e035872c50f048ffc7e014ce2a54326_tile_small.jpg"><img src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/sparkling-rose-eyes-romantic-curls_look_6e035872c50f048ffc7e014ce2a54326_tile_small.jpg?w=276" alt="sparkling-rose-eyes-romantic-curls_look_6e035872c50f048ffc7e014ce2a54326_tile_small" width="276" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-374" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">We know we are supposed to get 8 hours of sleep, but really, who can possibly accomplish that? And really, is there anything worse than your colleague telling you how tired you look? <em>Ugh.</em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">So we asked our extremely clever Preen.Me readers how they rescue their face when there is no time for a beauty nap:</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><ul>\n	<li>Cold tea bags and ice cubes on the eyes!!</li>\n	<li>Grated potatoes + grated cucumber + 1 tbs of milk: put all together and apply on eye zone for 10 minutes.</li>\n	<li>A good 7 coats of mascara and tons and tons of eye liner!!</li>\n	<li>Bronzer is the best gift for an insomniac.</li>\n	<li>Hourglass Diffused Light Powder under the eyes, attracts light and smooths the texture under the eye. I use it on brides all the time.</li>\n	<li>Whitening eye drops.</li>\n	<li>Always keep a spoon in your freezer instant face lift if you apply it first thing in the morning where your problem areas are.</li>\n	<li>I rub lemon on me entire face! It evens out skin tone, takes away blemishes and makes your pores super tight-you can actually feel it!</li>\n	<li>If I''m seriously rough looking (think finals week) I just rock a heavy smokey eye, teased hair, and something with studs and pretend to be in a punk band or something...</li>\n	<li>This sounds horrible, but dumping your face in a big bowl of ice water will really help to make that sullen no sleep look into a rosy refreshed wide awake morning. <em>(Sounds great if you ask us!)</em></li>\n	<li>Curl eyelashes to open up the eyes or better yet.... false eyelashes.</li>\n	<li>Luminizer and coffee.</li>\n	<li>BIG SUNGLASSES!!</li>\n</ul></font>\n<font SIZE="3">Here are some bright eyed looks to try next time your face needs a pick me up:</font>\n\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/11654032/small" width="310" height="400"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/15189006/small" width="310" height="400"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/11562543/small" width="310" height="400"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/6231360/small" width="310" height="400"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/6223253/small" width="310" height="400"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em><a href="http://preen.me">Preen.Me</a> is the world''s leading social beauty platform. Find brand new looks, how tos and video tutorials every single day. </em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em>Have your own great beauty looks to share? Upload them to <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> for your chance to be exposed to millions of people every week.</em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em></em><em>Find us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity?ref=hl">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/preendotme">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114026381779272019938/posts">Google+</a>.</em></font>', 'How To Fake 8 Hours Of Sleep', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-fake-8-hours-of-sleep', '', '', '2013-07-02 10:53:36', '2013-07-02 10:53:36', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=368', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(377, 1, '2013-07-02 14:17:46', '2013-07-02 14:17:46', '<font SIZE="3">Have you fallen into a beauty rut? Do you always grab the same lip gloss or mascara and run out the door? We all get attached to our makeup routines, but inside of every woman is an inner vixen just waiting to break free.</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">We asked what looks you would try if you had the courage. Here''s what you had to say and here \nsome inspiring looks to get you started (click on the photos for similar looks and the products you need):</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Jessica E. has been dying to dye her hair purple. Let''s give her some inspiration, shall we?</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/15377006"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/purple-to-pink-ombre-hair_look_ffd21e31de0dde2cda729d75e4043a4a_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Brandi said: "Bright colors that make a statement I''m addicted to nude colors &amp; nude shimmers."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/14126033"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/pink-and-black_look_cd31f7d2a855bf78ba3fffb8af014f67_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">For Tisa it was all about adding an extra finishing touch: "Super glam lashes...as long as they don''t look like caterpillars."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/17432002"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/lavender-coral-smoke_look_39bae8ca8a08497cd655055f41987787_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Ines wants to bring on the drama: "Dark eyes, dark lips."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/7963042"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/cat-eye-purple-lips_look_20983d960b975c9320764926e5870ac1_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">How ''bout some glam rock, as Kaity suggests: "I would try something either really glamorous like from the 80''s or attempt a Ziggy Stardust look."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/6231407"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bright-teal_look_77349e986db9e5547dc40eb9aecbd9b4_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Here''s one many shy girls would like to try. Keira said: "Red lips. I am scared to put any bright colour on my lips as I don''t like attention lol."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/13224001"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/sexy-red-lips_look_7f0b6ce68dcbcd3a78afe36757146f6b_look.jpg" width="200" height="85" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Elena was keen on testing out some editorial looks: "High Goth. A dramatic lip look (I tend to emphasize my eyes). High-drama, advertisement-style makeup. I want to start trying some special effects stuff, too."</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/1569988"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/black-blue_look_77542f2728d4cc24c5ce3371058f4f07_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">And finally, Valerie said "I would try going blond."\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/421254"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/fishtail-messy-bun_look_8efe482139e2c39507f24a4da6f43035_look.jpg" width="200" height="185" /></a></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em><a href="http://preen.me">Preen.Me</a> is the world''s leading social beauty platform. Find brand new looks, how tos and video tutorials every single day. </em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em>Have your own great beauty looks to share? Upload them to <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> for your chance to be exposed to millions of people every week.</em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em></em><em>Find us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity?ref=hl">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/preendotme">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114026381779272019938/posts">Google+</a>.</em></font>', 'Do You Have The Courage? Top Looks You Would Love To Try', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'do-you-have-the-courage-top-looks-you-would-love-to-try', '', '', '2013-07-02 14:17:46', '2013-07-02 14:17:46', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=377', 0, 'post', '', 0),
