(399, 1, '2013-07-05 10:48:59', '2013-07-05 10:48:59', '<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/asymmetrical-fringe_look_a6d1e13afc12830537e4eafd282a02ef_look.jpg"><img src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/asymmetrical-fringe_look_a6d1e13afc12830537e4eafd282a02ef_look.jpg?w=300" alt="asymmetrical-fringe_look_a6d1e13afc12830537e4eafd282a02ef_look" width="300" height="246" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-412" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Have you always wanted to take the leap and go boy-short but just haven''t been bold enough to face the shears? What if you had only two choices, to chop it off once or never again cut it again?</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">We put you guys to the test and asked our Preen.Me fans what they would do. The responses were, admittedly, surprising. The majority of you would take the leap and cut your hair (58%!) while the rest would choose to keep it long and flowy forever.\n\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/hairpie.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-402" alt="hairpie" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/hairpie.png?w=300" width="300" height="150" /></a></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Here are some inspirational looks for all of you. Don''t forget to click on the photo for similar looks, tutorials and products. Happy hairstyling!</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">For the long haired maidens:</font>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/11580005/small" height="496" width="310" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/1383393/small" height="310" width="310" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/15333006/small" height="400" width="310" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/11998053/small" height="310" width="310" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n\n<font SIZE="3">And some fantastic looks for the choppers:</font>\n<iframe src="http://www.pree