(415, 1, '2013-07-08 12:35:23', '2013-07-08 12:35:23', '<font SIZE="3"><a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/wecandoitimages.jpeg"><img src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/wecandoitimages.jpeg" alt="wecandoitimages" width="196" height="257" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-465" /></a></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Makeup is a powerful tool when it comes to self confidence. Tons of studies show that women wearing makeup are viewed as more trustworthy, likable and professional. It''s no wonder that we take time to enhance our features in the morning. Those extra few minutes mean we are worthy of bringing out our best features. We deserve to look our best.</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><a href="//‬www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity/posts/492043237534216">We asked our Preen.Me fans what products boost their confidence the most</a>. Below are the most popular responses along with amazing and easy looks that use these products. Try these out for the ultimate confidence booster!</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Want to recreate eyecatching looks with one easy glide? Try <a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1180039/">Urban Decay 24/7 Waterproof Liquid Eyeliner Perversion</a>:</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1180039/"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/udeyeliner310u7ubvdl.jpg" width="230" height="200" /></a>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1180039/#grid_related_looks"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/screen-shot-2013-07-08-at-2-58-34-pm.png" width="280" height="200" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Lifelong lipstick devotees swear by a timeless red pout to bring the bold from within. Try <a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1143300/">MAC Matte Lipstick in Russian Red</a>:</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1143300/"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/macreddownload.jpeg" width="230" height="230" /></a>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1143300/#grid_related_looks"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/screen-shot-2013-07-08-at-3-01-24-pm.png" width="280" height="200" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Mascara enhances a polished look which is a surefire way to boost confidence levels. Try <a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1035629/">NYX Doll Eye Mascara in Extreme Black</a>:</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1035629/"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nyxmasc614bvpdzd4l-_sl1000_.jpg" width="230" height="200" /></a>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1035629/#grid_related_looks"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/screen-shot-2013-07-08-at-3-02-43-pm.png" width="280" height="200" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">A dab of lip gloss will bring ultra shine and instantaeously boost your mood. Try <a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1114138/">NYX Mega Shine Lip Gloss:</a></font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1114138/"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nyxshine51uat9ja-5l-_sl1000_.jpg" width="230" height="200" /></a>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1114138/#grid_related_looks"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/screen-shot-2013-07-08-at-3-04-02-pm.png" width="280" height="200" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">When you feel bad about your appearance, false eyelashes will make you feel like a superstar. Try <a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1194005/">Ardell Invisiband Lashes</a>:</font>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1194005/"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/falsies510gn3wa59l.jpg" width="230" height="200" /></a>\n<a href="http://www.preen.me/product/1194005/#grid_related_looks"><img alt="Test" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/screen-shot-2013-07-08-at-3-11-55-pm.png" width="280" height="200" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Nothing wrong with covering up a few blemishes and dark circles to make us feel more attractive. Tr