(472, 1, '2013-07-09 13:38:23', '2013-07-09 13:38:23', '<span style="font-size:medium;">Yesterday, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity/posts/499379760133897">we asked you which makeup product gave you the most self-confidence</a>. Now it''s time to take a look at the crazy, zany, and just plain strange beauty items that you can buy online.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">We''re not sure what''s weirder, the fact someone came up with these wacky inventions, or the fact that some people actually buy them. We bet you didn''t even know these existed!</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Here are the top 10 wackiest beauty products:</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">1. Everyone loves nachos, right? So why not slather some ooey gooey Nacho Cheese-flavored Lip Balm? We bet you''re dying to try it:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nacho-lip-balm-10-photolist.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-474" alt="nacho-lip-balm-10-photolist" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nacho-lip-balm-10-photolist.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="200" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">2. Time to style your hair. With the Pistol Hair Dryer you''ll be ready to roll like a badass:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/pistolimages.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-475" alt="pistolimages" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/pistolimages.jpeg?w=300" width="300" height="250" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">3. No, those aren''t clumpy lashes! Artist Jessica Harrison takes dead fly legs and glues them on for an unforgettable flutter:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/a97496_fly.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-527" alt="a97496_Fly" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/a97496_fly.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="237" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">4. Makeup for your legs!? You got that right. With Aspa''s spray-on nylons, who needs to worry about runs and tears:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/aspa-nylons-meia-calca-spray-instantnea-compre-2-leve-3_mlb-o-195083367_9500-1.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-476" alt="aspa-nylons-meia-calca-spray-instantnea-compre-2-leve-3_MLB-O-195083367_9500 (1)" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/aspa-nylons-meia-calca-spray-instantnea-compre-2-leve-3_mlb-o-195083367_9500-1.jpg?w=300" width="270" height="300" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">5. There''s nothing like the sweet smell of a Funeral Home (Demeter Fragrance Library) to keep you fresh:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/funeral_home_fragrance.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-477" alt="_funeral_home_fragrance" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/funeral_home_fragrance.jpg?w=300" width="223" height="300" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">6. While you''re at it, don''t forget to do your nails. StrangeBeautiful came out with a line of polishes - Volume V - inspired by menstrual blood and bruises (yes, you read that right):</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nail.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-478" alt="nail" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/nail.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">7. And straight from Japan... Here''s a new exercise toy for your lips! Now we can all have that perfect pout with the Face Slimmer:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/japanese-mouth-exerciser.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-479" alt="japanese-mouth-exerciser" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/japanese-mouth-exerciser.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="235" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">8. Dazzle everyone with Smile Gems'' diamond-encrusted teeth! For a smile that''s literally worth a million bucks:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/teethimages.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-480" alt="teethimages" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/teethimages.jpeg?w=300" width="250" height="196" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">9. Who knew you could eat your way to bigger breasts? Apparently, there''s a cookie in Japan - the F-Cup Cookie- that claims to do just that:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/fcupimages.jpeg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-481" alt="fcupimages" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/fcupimages.jpeg?w=300" width="250" height="202" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">10. After your long night out, you''re ready to hit the hay. Keep those boobs smooth with a special anti-wrinkle pillow known as the Bosom Buddy:</span>\n<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bosom-buddy-1-e1326853007568.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-482" alt="Bosom-Buddy-1-e1326853007568" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bosom-buddy-1-e1326853007568.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="250" /></a>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Know any other wacky products? Tell us here by commenting below.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em><a href="http://preen.me">Preen.Me</a> is the world''s leading social beauty platform. Find brand new looks, how tos and video tutorials every single day.</em></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em>Have your own great beauty looks to share? Upload them to <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> for your chance to be exposed to millions of people every week.</em></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em></em><em>Find us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity?ref=hl">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/preendotme">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114026381779272019938/posts">Google+</a>.</em></span>\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n<link href="http://cdn-images.mailchimp.com/embedcode/slim-081711.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">\n<style type="text/css">\n	#mc_embed_signup{background:#fff; clear:left; font:14px Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; }\n	/* Add your own MailChimp form style overrides in your site stylesheet or in this style block.\n	   We recommend moving this block and the preceding CSS link to the HEAD of your HTML file. */\n</style>\n<div id="mc_embed_signup">\n<form action="http://preen.us6.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=d53ec6e74bf3544c4030bf6d3&amp;id=abfb47a775" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>\n	<label for="mce-EMAIL">Subscribe to the Preen.Me emails!</label>\n	<input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="email" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="email address" required>\n	<div class="clear"><input type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button"></div>\n</form>\n</div>\n\n<!--End mc_embed_signup-->', 'The Top 10 Wackiest Beauty Products!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-top-10-wackiest-beauty-products', '', '', '2013-07-09 13:38:23', '2013-07-09 13:38:23', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=472', 0, 'post', '', 1),
