(530, 1, '2013-07-12 10:50:08', '2013-07-12 10:50:08', '<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/eastwest.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-465" alt="wecandoitimages" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/eastwest.jpg" width="165" height="220" /></a>\n\n<font SIZE="3">We here at <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> love bringing bicoastal beauties together through our mutual love of looking fabulous. But sometimes we like to have some fun and instigate a harmless (i.e. no gangs!) rivalry.</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">So....LET THE BATTLE BEGIN! We sorted through over 1 million user preferences and 100,000+ looks to see which top eye looks distinguish the two coasts. We were surprised! We thought west coasters were too casual and free-flowing to go glam and east coasters were too formal for au-natural. As you can see below, there is apparently no merit to these generalizations.</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3">And don''t worry, we haven''t forgotten about our neighbors in the middle. Next installment: North vs South! Here''s wishing everyone a happy beauty routine no matter what our longitudinal differences may be...</font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em>East Coast Beauties either love Kim K glam or daytime sass. Click on the photos to see more looks to strut the city streets with:</em></font>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/1578041/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/1405393/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/116062/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/5356052/small" width="200" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em>West Coast Beauties love the drama! Click on the photos to see more looks that work with a beachside cocktail: </em></font>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/595100/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe> \n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/314112/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>  \n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/1378587/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n<iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/990201/small" width="270" height="300"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\n\n<font SIZE="3">Are you a beach bum, city girl, a sassy country beauty? Tell us about the beauty trends you notice in your town in the comments section below.</font>\n\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em><a href="http://preen.me">Preen.Me</a> is the world''s leading social beauty platform. Find brand new looks, how tos and video tutorials every single day.</em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em>Have your own great beauty looks to share? Upload them to <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> for your chance to be exposed to millions of people every week.</em></font>\n\n<font SIZE="3"><em></em><em>Find us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity?ref=hl">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/preendotme">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114026381779272019938/posts">Google+</a>.</em></font>', 'East Coast vs. West Coast! The Battle of The Top Eye Look', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'east-coast-vs-west-coast-the-battle-of-the-top-eye-look', '', '', '2013-07-12 10:50:08', '2013-07-12 10:50:08', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=530', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(560, 1, '2013-07-13 07:51:10', '2013-07-13 07:51:10', '<a title="The Preen.Me Blog" href="http://blog.preen.me">The Preen.Me blog</a> is looking to feature new guest writers and you''re invited.\n\nPreen.Me is the world''s leading social beauty platform. We have brand new looks and tutorials every single day, as well as a blog that showcases beauty content from unique point of view. We have over 1.6 million fans on our Facebook community site Beauty Addicts so as a guest blogger you would get loads of love!\n\nFor blog content we are looking for compelling and unique pieces surrounding beauty, women, and the makeup experience.\n\nKeep in mind, for the blog we are not looking for product reviews or tutorials. If you do have a tutorial or look that you want to share, you can <a title="Upload your beauty look to Preen.Me!" href="http://www.preen.me/uploadlook/#/upload">upload it to Preen.Me</a>. If we feature the look your work will be shared with all of our fans!\n\nHere are some potential idea starters:\n\n- Out of the ordinary beauty experimentations.\n\n- A light piece on any historical or scientific context on beauty.\n\n- A light and fun story about your personal beauty experience.\n\n- A case study of a habit-forming beauty routine that you are trying to break free from.\n\nIf you have a topic you''d like to explore, please send us a draft (or even a quick outline) in an email to: info@preen.me\n\nWe''d love to hear from you!\n\nIf you read up to this point, here are some tips when writing:\n<ul>\n	<li>Keep the structure simple</li>\n	<li>Read the article out loud</li>\n	<li>Read your sources and don’t say something that they didn’t say</li>\n	<li>Use trustworthy sources, not personal blogs, Yahoo Answers, or Wikipedia for anything but general knowledge</li>\n	<li>Mine the sources for the most incredible information and ditch everything else</li>\n	<li>Spell check</li>\n	<li>Start the intro with a joke or something clever. Don’t waste time introducing the subject.</li>\n	<li>Keep biases out</li>\n	<li>Don’t be time sensitive</li>\n	<li>Don’t use other people’s jokes</li>\n</ul>\n<a href="http://preen.me"><img class="size-medium wp-image-564" alt="Preen.Me: the world’s leading social beauty platform. " src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/bastats-2-a.jpg?w=300" width="300" height="300" /></a>\n', 'Write a Guest Post in the World''s Leading Social Beauty Platform!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'write-a-guest-post-in-the-worlds-leading-social-beauty-platform', '', '', '2013-07-13 07:51:10', '2013-07-13 07:51:10', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?page_id=560', 0, 'page', '', 0),
