(1163, 1, '2013-08-01 22:43:52', '2013-08-01 22:43:52', '<span style="font-size:medium;">As much as we love to take beauty risks on a daily basis, job interviews are the one occasion we may need to dial it down a bit. As the economy improves, unemployment is still low and the job market is very competitive. Preparation is key in this cutting edge market.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Here are five simple beauty recommendations to stay classy and sophisticated for your next job interview:</span>\n<h2 style="text-align:left;">1. Hair</h2>\n[caption id="attachment_1214" align="alignright" width="230"]<a title="Lisa''s updo for your interview" href="http://www.preen.me/look/359085" target="_blank" rel="http://www.preen.me/profile/342077"><img class="wp-image-1214   " title="The updo for your interview" alt="folded-hair_look_4fc0fe42eed16a9c1d573eb924872ba0_look" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/folded-hair_look_4fc0fe42eed16a9c1d573eb924872ba0_look.jpg?w=300" width="230" height="230" /></a> Updo by Lisa A.[/caption]\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Preparing for a job interview is a good incentive to consider a new style. It need not be dramatic, just a modern update of a style that flatters you.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">When interviewing for a job, it''s good to make sure that your hairstyle is flattering but not complicated. Pastel and other colors such as purple or blue (unfortunately!) should not be part of your interview hair do. Even if Manic Panic-chic is your thing , it''s best not to advertise it right off the bat. You can just wait until the weekend to get your pink ombre tips on. </span>\n<h2 style="text-align:left;"></h2>\n[caption id="attachment_1279" align="alignleft" width="210"]<a href="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/metallic-golden-eyes-peachy-nude-lips_look_fea2b5521e4ef5f842c052cc73b6582d_look-1.jpg"><img class="wp-image-1279 " alt="Makeup by Naseem D" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/metallic-golden-eyes-peachy-nude-lips_look_fea2b5521e4ef5f842c052cc73b6582d_look-1.jpg?w=300" width="210" height="210" /></a> Makeup by Naseem D[/caption]\n<h2></h2>\n<h2>2. Skin Repair</h2>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Some of us are guilty of spending way too many hours at the beach. But we do have many choices for restoring a youthful appearance to our skin. A daily skin care routine that includes products for exfoliation, brightening and protection from the sun. Experts say results began to show within one or two months - so plan ahead!</span>\n<h2 style="text-align:left;">3. Wardrobe Change</h2>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">What you wear to a job interview has an immediate impact on the impression you make. For those new to the job market, most of your college wardrobe will be too casual for business attire. Sadly, it''s time to put the jean shorts and flip flops back in the closet. Business wear should replace jeans and short skirts no matter how great your legs are or how hot it is. But there is no need to fret! Dressing for success has never been more fun. Mix bright colored heels with your suit. Add a black blazer over your business casual sundress. A cute new belt will be your new best friend.</span>\n<h2 style="text-align:left;">4. Your Smile<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/1111043"><img class="wp-image-1217 alignright" title="Jolani J.''s Smile" alt="why-so-serious-smile_look_70ec3645eb7941718a4ba075eb9fb825_look" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/07/why-so-serious-smile_look_70ec3645eb7941718a4ba075eb9fb825_look.jpg?w=150" width="252" height="208" /></a></h2>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">If eyes are the widows to the soul, it is the smile that gives them shine. Your smile should be bright and white. Teeth whitening kits are available over-the-counter in stores or you can choose to have them whitened professionally.</span>\n<h2>5. The Right Beauty Looks</h2>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">When interviewing for a job, the goal should not be only to look good but to match your makeup to the occasion. Different looks position your differently and it is important  send the right message. Here are some of our suggestions:</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><strong>Executive:</strong></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><strong><em></em></strong>When you want to convey managerial and leadership while still looking good, strong colored eyes, naked lips and an updo will fit.</span>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1312" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/10887022"><img class=" wp-image-1312  " alt="Jolani J. Lips" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/red-velvet_look_8ebb0d20b73675f6c375be98f9182c00_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Jolani J. Lips[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1313" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/15237001"><img class=" wp-image-1313  " alt="Hiardo By Tina L." src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/upside-down-french-braid-bun_look_413d517accb98bf2777db31a0d4fbf77_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Hiardo By Tina L.[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1315" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/16573005"><img class=" wp-image-1315 " alt="Eyebrows by Brittany K. " src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/eyebrow-tutorial_look_e0100ebe3cbe5c60435dfbb90bfd8b31_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Eyebrows by Brittany K.[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><strong>Entry-level:</strong></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Being new but eager to learn, conveying fresh and untried ideas can be expressed with bright eyeshadow and noticeable lipstick.</span>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1304" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/15312005"><img class=" wp-image-1304  " alt="soul-mate_look_a7fae0ba150ff6e01930abf4631c4ef4_look" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/soul-mate_look_a7fae0ba150ff6e01930abf4631c4ef4_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Nails by Iliana[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1305" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/18816008"><img class=" wp-image-1305  " alt="beautiful-waterfall-braid_look_3e4804445c153e67bd06fd144f7fac29_look" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/beautiful-waterfall-braid_look_3e4804445c153e67bd06fd144f7fac29_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Waterfall Braid by Holi M.[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1307" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/16323010"><img class=" wp-image-1307  " alt="Lips by Jessica B." src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/fuller-lips-tutorial_look_3c267d5ab48cb35766e500c82e283c1f_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Lips by Jessica B.[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style="font-size:medium;">Formal:</span></strong>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Toning it down in the broader sense would mean less colors but distinguished. formal envirment</span>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1290" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/18901005"><img class=" wp-image-1290  " alt="Marta M.''s Makeup" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/natural-look_look_ef5f0a4f0d16197feda86dd03cced51d_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Marta M.''s Makeup[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1293" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/18403001"><img class=" wp-image-1293  " title="Franch Twist by Tina L." alt="french-twist-around-ponytail-hairstyle_look_c77ea0a458bbe381c484cf8b25e0f653_look" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/french-twist-around-ponytail-hairstyle_look_c77ea0a458bbe381c484cf8b25e0f653_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Franch Twist by Tina L.[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1311" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/18576003"><img class="wp-image-1311  " alt="Annie C. Loreal Nailpolish" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/vip-status_look_ae0658db3507785b9af7339783c33080_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Annie C. Loreal Nailpolish[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><strong>Showy:</strong></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Putting yourself out there with bold charismatic colors that compliments your unique style.</span>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1309" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/10247094"><img class=" wp-image-1309 " alt="Jittaun W" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/summer-goddess_look_a1a992e2ec39bee7dc931c8eb4a2e79a_look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Jittaun W[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1308" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/22484001"><img class=" wp-image-1308 " alt="Jolani J." src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/hazed_look_916d7af9bf3250aebdda8e937a936d63_look-1.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Jolani J.[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_1310" align="alignleft" width="150"]<a href="http://www.preen.me/look/116062"><img class=" wp-image-1310 " alt="Makeup by Kim Kardashian" src="http://preenme.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/look.jpg?w=150" width="150" height="150" /></a> Makeup by Kim Kardashian[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Have more tips? Share them with us in the comments below.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em><a href="http://preen.me">Preen.Me</a> is the world''s leading social beauty platform. Find brand new looks, how tos and video tutorials every single day.</em></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em>Have your own great beauty looks to share? Upload them to <a href="http://www.preen.me">Preen.Me</a> for your chance to be exposed to millions of people every week.</em></span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><em></em><em>Find us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BeautyAddictsCommunity?ref=hl">Facebook</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/preendotme">Twitter</a> and <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/114026381779272019938/posts">Google+</a>.</em></span>', 'Five Beauty Tips for Landing a Job', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'five-beauty-tips-for-landing-a-job', '', '', '2013-08-01 22:43:52', '2013-08-01 22:43:52', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=1163', 0, 'post', '', 0);
