(1432, 1, '2013-08-05 08:21:00', '2013-08-05 08:21:00', '<h5 style="float:right;margin:10px;"></h5>\n<h2>Your Nails Have Only One Chance To Make A First Impression</h2>\n<h5><iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/21796010/small" width="310" height="496"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></h5>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Whenever you meet someone, the usual gesture is that you shake hands with them. In the process, your nails are instantly noticeable. Take a look at your nails; Are they properly shaped and free of dents? When was the last time you did something for your nails? Poorly kept nails leave a bad impression on the people around you and whilst it is an area most overlooked by people, it is vital for you to make sure your nails are looking good at all times!</span>\n<h3>Cleaning and Keeping Your Nails Healthy</h3>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">We will start by looking at some easy to follow steps to get cleaner and healthier nails. If you are one of those people that are guilty of biting nails, then you’re about to hear some bad news. Refraining from biting nails not only gives you longer nails to play with but also it will also protect you from bacterial and fungal infections. Secondly, make sure you wash your hands using an antibacterial soap and clean your nails using a soft nailbrush to get rid of dirt below the nails.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Whilst it may not seem entirely necessary, try to make a conscious effort in wearing gloves whenever doing tasks that involve a lot of water and strong chemicals. So next time you go around doing your dishes or cleaning your yard, remember that these substances can have a bad effect on the appearance of nails.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Having healthy eating habit is also an integral part in keeping your nails strong. Make sure your diet contains enough calcium to avoid your nails from becoming weak and tearable, but also learn what <a href="http://www.wikihow.com/Improve-Hair-and-Nails-Through-Your-Diet" target="_blank">effects other foods will have</a>.  A final thing you can do is make sure your hands are well moisturized with a vitamin-filled moisturiser, whilst making sure that you massage it into the cuticles as well.</span>\n<h3>Maintaining Your Nails</h3>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">With the prep work for nice nails out the way, your next focus should be on how to maintain their look. Firstly, whilst cutting your nails, make sure that you always trim them straight across as you can always give a little roundedness to the shape to the tip afterwards. Once you’re happy with the length, it’s now time to shape your nails with a file, taking care to keep it moving in the same direction. Push back your cuticles and trim them with a cuticle cutter if you notice any dead skin or ragged ends the leave the base of the nail. To get an overall smooth surface of your nails, buff them using a nail buffer. This will boost the blood flow in the nail bed, which helps to grow strong and healthy nails.</span>\n<h5 style="float:right;margin:10px;"><iframe src="http://www.preen.me/embed/look/1414773/small" width="310" height="496"  frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></h5>\n<span style="font-size:medium;">Once you have followed the above steps, your nails should be ready to be polished. First, put a thin layer of nail hardener on your nails, and once they are dry you can put some colored nail polish on them.  Make sure you apply a thin, even layer and once dry you may want to add another coat for a more even appearance or more intense colour. You may want to finish off by putting a clear coat over the top of nails to avoid chipping and to keep them looking shiny and noticeable. You may wish to get a little more creative with nails by using <a href="http://www.roobeauty.com/section.php/583/1/nail-art-supplies" target="_blank">glitters and other nail art</a>, and this will certainly give people the impression that you’re a unique individual.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;">It doesn’t take long to keep your nails looking nice, so you’ll want to refrain from cheating too much by going to salons for a professional manicure. They contain strong chemicals that can lead to chronic nail bed infections. The perfect looking nails are well within your grasp, it just takes a little prep work to get them to a level that you just need to try to maintain.</span>\n\n<span style="font-size:medium;"><strong>About the Author:</strong> <em>Rhonda Davis is a nail art blogger who loves to share tips on how to create the best looking nail art that can be easily recreated.</em></span>\n\n<section id="imageStrip_teaserLooks">\n<h3></h3>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>WANT MORE NAILS?</h3>\n<div>\n<div><a title="Beached Nails" href="http://www.preen.me/look/21401004"><img class="alignleft" alt="Beached Nails" src="http://cd9e886051ff950d0f56-cbae8bdcbe387ea986370e0eac63e3b5.r93.cf1.rackcdn.com/beached-nails_look_6be8ea8c27b55f1d4fef6f70980fb9c2_tile_small.jpg" width="86" height="86" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a title="Marbled with Bling Bow" href="http://www.preen.me/look/22246001"><img class="alignleft" alt="Marbled with Bling Bow" src="http://cd9e886051ff950d0f56-cbae8bdcbe387ea986370e0eac63e3b5.r93.cf1.rackcdn.com/marbled-with-bling-bow_look_d39924ec201aaaaf4870df7ce8d8341a_tile_small.jpg" width="86" height="86" /></a></div>\n<div><a title="Limon Ada" href="http://www.preen.me/look/22189002"><img class="alignleft" alt="Limon Ada" src="http://cd9e886051ff950d0f56-cbae8bdcbe387ea986370e0eac63e3b5.r93.cf1.rackcdn.com/limon-ada_look_63fc3d75b5e41c7631373b2cb6b7af04_tile_small.jpg" width="86" height="86" /></a></div>\n</div>\n</section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section></section><section><a title="Nail Looks on Preen.Me" href="http://www.preen.me/tag/nails/">View More</a></section>', 'How To Keep Your Nails Looking Beautiful', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-keep-your-nails-looking-beautiful', '', '', '2013-08-05 08:21:00', '2013-08-05 08:21:00', '', 0, 'http://blog.preen.me/?p=1432', 0, 'post', '', 0),
